{"parents": [{"link": "../", "title": "All classes"}], "prev": {"link": "../class_missingnode/", "title": "MissingNode"}, "next": {"link": "../class_multimeshinstance2d/", "title": "MultiMeshInstance2D"}, "title": "ModifierBoneTarget3D", "meta": {"github_url": "hide"}, "body": "<section id=\"modifierbonetarget3d\">\n<span id=\"class-modifierbonetarget3d\"></span><h1>ModifierBoneTarget3D<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#modifierbonetarget3d\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h1>\n<p><strong>Inherits:</strong> <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_skeletonmodifier3d/#class-skeletonmodifier3d\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">SkeletonModifier3D</span></a> <strong>&lt;</strong> <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_node3d/#class-node3d\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">Node3D</span></a> <strong>&lt;</strong> <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_node/#class-node\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">Node</span></a> <strong>&lt;</strong> <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_object/#class-object\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">Object</span></a></p>\n<p>\u0410 node that dynamically copies the 3D transform of a bone in its parent <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_skeleton3d/#class-skeleton3d\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">Skeleton3D</span></a>.</p>\n<section class=\"classref-introduction-group\" id=\"description\">\n<h2>Description<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#description\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>\n<p>This node selects a bone in a <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_skeleton3d/#class-skeleton3d\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">Skeleton3D</span></a> and attaches to it. This means that the <strong>ModifierBoneTarget3D</strong> node will dynamically copy the 3D transform of the selected bone.</p>\n<p>The functionality is similar to <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_boneattachment3d/#class-boneattachment3d\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">BoneAttachment3D</span></a>, but this node adopts the <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_skeletonmodifier3d/#class-skeletonmodifier3d\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">SkeletonModifier3D</span></a> cycle and is intended to be used as another <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_skeletonmodifier3d/#class-skeletonmodifier3d\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">SkeletonModifier3D</span></a>'s target.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"classref-reftable-group\" id=\"properties\">\n<h2>Properties<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#properties\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>\n<table class=\"docutils align-default\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"row-odd\"><td><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_int/#class-int\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">int</span></a></p></td>\n<td><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#class-modifierbonetarget3d-property-bone\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">bone</span></a></p></td>\n<td><p><code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">-1</span></code></p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-even\"><td><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_string/#class-string\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">String</span></a></p></td>\n<td><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#class-modifierbonetarget3d-property-bone-name\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">bone_name</span></a></p></td>\n<td><p><code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">&quot;&quot;</span></code></p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>\n<hr class=\"classref-section-separator docutils\" />\n<section class=\"classref-descriptions-group\" id=\"property-descriptions\">\n<h2>Property Descriptions<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#property-descriptions\" title=\"Link to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2>\n<p class=\"classref-property\" id=\"class-modifierbonetarget3d-property-bone\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_int/#class-int\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">int</span></a> <strong>bone</strong> = <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">-1</span></code> <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#class-modifierbonetarget3d-property-bone\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">\ud83d\udd17</span></a></p>\n<ul class=\"classref-property-setget simple\">\n<li><p><abbr title=\"No return value.\">void</abbr> <strong>set_bone</strong>(value: <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_int/#class-int\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">int</span></a>)</p></li>\n<li><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_int/#class-int\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">int</span></a> <strong>get_bone</strong>()</p></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The index of the attached bone.</p>\n<hr class=\"classref-item-separator docutils\" />\n<p class=\"classref-property\" id=\"class-modifierbonetarget3d-property-bone-name\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_string/#class-string\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">String</span></a> <strong>bone_name</strong> = <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">&quot;&quot;</span></code> <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#class-modifierbonetarget3d-property-bone-name\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">\ud83d\udd17</span></a></p>\n<ul class=\"classref-property-setget simple\">\n<li><p><abbr title=\"No return value.\">void</abbr> <strong>set_bone_name</strong>(value: <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_string/#class-string\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">String</span></a>)</p></li>\n<li><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../class_string/#class-string\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">String</span></a> <strong>get_bone_name</strong>()</p></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The name of the attached bone.</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n", "metatags": "<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["classes/class_multimeshinstance2d", "MultiMeshInstance2D", "N", "next"], ["classes/class_missingnode", "MissingNode", "P", "previous"]], "sourcename": "classes/class_modifierbonetarget3d.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a clas